      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS LOUELLA (4) finds it hard to break through. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (23.27) at this track. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Can measure up this time. RED OPAL (5) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (22.86) at this track in a Mix 3/4 over 400m. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Leading chance. SUNSHINE LILY (1) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing sixth (19.94) at Bulli in a Mix 3/4. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the rails draw. Expected to bounce back to best. IRON LADY (2) can feature with the right run.",
